data.description: Centrally located in this community, this concrete block and stucco Citation is waiting for a new owner.  Pavers on driveway and walkway.  Open split floor plan with a den (French Doors) right off of the living room.  Popular floor plan.  Kitchen features newer stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar, closet pantry and large dining area.  Designer wall colors throughout.  Beautiful island shutters throughout home plus in enclosed lanai.  Laminate flooring in heavy traffic areas with ceramic tile in wet areas.  Bonus room, however, laundry can be brought back into the house from the garage.  Climate controlled enclosed lanai (acrylic windows) with carpeting on the floor.  Island shutters to the north and woven woods w/wood molding to the east end.  Grilling patio.  Oversized 2-car garage with utility sink, privacy screens and washer & dryer.  Shingles 2020.  HVAC 2015.  Home has been re-piped.   Furniture is available under separate package.
